when I came back from my run.

00:06.484 --> 00:07.790
DANTE: I was just checking out
the old neighborhood.

00:07.964 --> 00:09.792
Dante, you need to go.

00:09.966 --> 00:11.924
Who the hell are you?I heard you were looking...
For me.

00:12.099 --> 00:14.710
Patel? I'm looking
for this dickhead.
Name's Arlo.

00:14.884 --> 00:18.322
We were hoping
to find my stash
before you got home.

00:18.496 --> 00:21.456
You underestimated her.
So Mr. Knox prefer
I take over the day-to-day,

00:21.630 --> 00:23.501
have I made myself clear?Yes.

00:23.675 --> 00:25.547
SYD: What do you want?It's what
Mr. Knox wants.

00:25.721 --> 00:26.896
You're gonna be
taught a lesson.

00:27.070 --> 00:29.203
I'm coming after
someone you care about.

00:29.377 --> 00:30.508
NANCY: You said over
the phone something
about time, right?

00:30.682 --> 00:32.554
Twenty-four hours,
give or take.

00:32.728 --> 00:34.860
Hey, it's Syd.ARLO: This isn't
a personal number.

00:35.035 --> 00:37.124
How'd you get it?I have a knack
for finding people.

00:37.298 --> 00:39.300
Okay, let's meet.

00:39.474 --> 00:41.998
Hey, Kat! I just wanna
introduce you to Syd.

00:42.172 --> 00:45.262
Syd?ARLO: You're not the only
one who can find people.

00:45.436 --> 00:47.134
[CELL PHONE RINGS]MAN: Put it down.
You should've answered.

00:47.308 --> 00:49.745
It's about your son.

00:49.919 --> 00:50.963
SHAUNA: Dante, there
are men here with guns.
They're threatening Zach.

00:51.138 --> 00:53.096
[GUNSHOT][PEOPLE SCREAMING]

00:58.406 --> 01:00.364
What the hell
did you just do?

01:00.538 --> 01:02.801
