my daughter has been shot.

01:06.196 --> 01:07.850
I'm looking for
Katherine Vaughn Miller!

01:08.024 --> 01:09.199
Kat is your daughter?

01:11.071 --> 01:12.289
I'm looking for my daughter!

01:16.859 --> 01:18.948
♪♪♪♪

01:28.479 --> 01:31.308
MAN: Stop. No.
Just listen to me.

01:31.482 --> 01:33.745
DJ: 36 minutes
past the hour.

01:33.919 --> 01:35.007
The Russ Carr Morning Show.
Good morning, everybody.
How you doing?

01:35.182 --> 01:37.184
[INDISTINCT ARGUING]

01:37.358 --> 01:39.621
GIRL: I wonder
what he did this time.

01:39.795 --> 01:40.665
Does it matter?

01:40.839 --> 01:42.058
Yes.

01:43.146 --> 01:44.191
Nah.

01:44.365 --> 01:46.106
They've been like this.

01:46.280 --> 01:48.369
I think this one is real,
though.

01:48.543 --> 01:50.762
What does that mean?

01:50.936 --> 01:52.721
Nothing.

01:52.895 --> 01:54.331
Just don't look.

01:54.505 --> 01:56.246
Here.
Look at me.

01:57.247 --> 01:58.205
That's dumb.

01:58.944 --> 02:00.381
Then why you smiling?

02:00.555 --> 02:01.860
I'm not.

02:02.034 --> 02:04.298
Fine.
Don't do it.
Don't smile.

02:04.472 --> 02:05.864
Don't smile.

02:06.038 --> 02:08.084
[GIGGLES]

02:08.258 --> 02:09.259
Told you
you were smiling.

02:09.433 --> 02:10.782
You're still dumb.

02:11.870 --> 02:13.568
Mom?Not now, baby.

02:14.177 --> 02:15.700
We got a long drive.

02:16.701 --> 02:18.050
Daddy!

02:18.225 --> 02:19.748
Syd. Marcus.
We're gonna work this out.

02:19.922 --> 02:21.184
Everything
is gonna be okay.

02:21.358 --> 02:23.186
Daddy,
I don't want to go.

02:24.753 --> 02:26.407
I'll see you real soon,
baby girl.

02:26.581 --> 02:27.930
You too, Marcus.

02:28.104 --> 02:29.845
I'm gonna come
and visit real soon.
I promise.

02:30.411 --> 02:31.890
Yeah.

02:32.064 --> 02:33.109
Okay, Dad.

02:34.066 --> 02:35.894
[ENGINE STARTS]

02:36.068 --> 02:38.158
♪♪♪♪

02:48.559 --> 02:49.952
DOCTOR: Your daughter's
out of surgery.

02:51.040 --> 02:52.694
We're not completely
out of the woods yet.

02:52.868 --> 02:54.783
She's young.
Strong.

02:54.957 --> 02:56.219
Is she gonna
be okay?

02:56.393 --> 02:57.699
We've done
everything we can.

02:57.873 --> 02:59.396
At this point,
all signs are positive,

02:59.570 --> 03:01.224
and there's nothing
to do but wait.

03:01.398 --> 03:02.965
It'll be a few hours
before she's up.

03:04.184 --> 03:05.185
Thanks.Mmm-hmm.

03:08.144 --> 03:09.972
WOMAN: [ON PA]
Oxney, please call the page.

03:10.146 --> 03:12.279
Oxney, call the page operator.

03:22.289 --> 03:24.465
Orderly to ICU.

03:24.639 --> 03:26.075
Orderly to ICU, please.

03:26.249 --> 03:27.685
I saw her file.

03:29.470 --> 03:30.775
Katherine.

03:31.776 --> 03:33.778
She's a year
older than me.

03:33.952 --> 03:36.390
Syd, I...I guess we know
what the straw was

03:36.564 --> 03:38.000
that finally broke
Mama's back.

03:40.002 --> 03:41.482
I knew
you were a cheater.

03:42.657 --> 03:44.049
